{"tid":625943,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保方老將最後一屆就大曬咩","createTime":"2018-04-11T20:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T14:03:23.000Z","uid":36324,"like":340,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"ff363f8d1af016808d075c49ef814d9211911965","tid":625943,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T20:55:14.000Z","msg":"踢左二十鳩幾年職業足球，隊友咁明顯犯規之後咁樣 on99 走去兇球證屌球證推撞球證，之後紅牌都可以話黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔紅就真係黑啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係以為米高奧利華後生會俾面你下話，如果有咁既思維根本就係廢老思維 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要咁多 on9 盲撐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆賓拿迪亞應該兩黃一紅埋添啦，都已經走甩左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (奧利華都唔知係唔記得定廢時刺激祖記D人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n從後飛撞 --&gt; 黃<br />\n破壞明顯入球機會 --&gt; 紅 --&gt; 新例全餐減刑 --&gt; 黃<br />\n<br />\n條友幾分鐘前先一條友搞低兩個攞黃牌，呢下平心都一定兩黃一紅"},{"pid":"51d6e5e52521e1043f12d6ee252f5365269e6b06","tid":625943,"uid":19556,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T20:56:28.000Z","msg":"年年都最後一屆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f070ab1d05a9457b96be5a9ea74e9fbd499f3f5","tid":625943,"uid":129536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T20:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img